descriptions: You can download a trial version of this app to try it for 30 minutes for free.
You won’t be charged anything when this free trial ends. You can’t make in-app purchases or use add-on content during this free trial, but you’ll keep any achievements you earn.

display_long_description:
Step into a unique VR campaign experience, blending immersive storytelling, intense action, and physics-based mechanics. 

In Personal 1, you play as an overworked office employee trapped in endless monotony. Seeking escape, you put on VR glasses to play your normal game and you end up in a vibrant cyberpunk world. But nothing is as it seems. Switching between the mundane office and a dynamic virtual future, you’ll gain unexpected abilities, face thrilling challenges, and uncover a mystery that blurs the line between reality and simulation.

With a powerful arsenal: pistols, rifles, grenades, and knives, and highly interactive physics, the game immerses you in environments where nearly everything can be interacted with. Solve puzzles, collect hidden trophies, and battle enemies while exploring richly detailed low-poly worlds. The story-driven campaign keeps you intrigued with its secrets and twists, while rewards like easter eggs motivate you to explore every corner.

With its gripping narrative, adrenaline-filled combat, and innovative mechanics, Personal 1 offers an unforgettable journey. Are you ready to uncover the truth?
